About Us
Our Company
Who We Are
About Us
We, at Minerva Mobile Home Park, say a warm welcome to you! If you are looking for a 55 and older retirement community in Haines City, Florida, look no further because we are here. Located near shopping, dining, entertainment, and medical amenities, our community provides the convenience of everything within proximity to our residents. At Minerva, we aim to offer our residents a clean, safe, and inexpensive living environment. The community has large lots and cozy mobile housing, some of which are also available for sale. We provide a wide range of on-site amenities like laundry facilities, a clubhouse, shuffleboard courts, and horseshoe areas. Our two ponds offer incredible views and awesome fishing.
Our committed personnel tirelessly work to preserve our community and see that the needs of the residents are met. Our goal is to provide an environment conducive to an active lifestyle with support and interaction. We would like to welcome you to become a member of our Minerva family if you want to find a quiet and cheap Florida retirement. Contact us and we will share details of available homes and lots, amenities, community rules, and leasing instructions. It would be our pleasure to have you come over and we would be delighted to show you around and tell you about what a great neighborhood is our community.
Contact Us
Our Mission
The goal of Minerva Mobile Home Park is to enhance the quality of life of senior residents through an affordable, entertaining lifestyle in a well-kept home with a clean, safe environment. We strive towards developing an enriching home environment that is well-accepting, accommodating, and developing, and residents can enjoy their socio-economic, self-interests as they grow old.
Our staff works to keep the facilities spotless, ensuring you build surrounding connections via activities and events, enabling continuing education and wellness programming, and ensuring 24-hour maintenance for our residents’ comfort and security. Senior living facility arguments should be supported by strong guidelines that guarantee all people live with dignity and respect. Our mission is to serve as a reliable ally whose main objective is to assist seniors in realizing their dreams of happy retirement years.
Home Is Where You
Park It
Welcome to Minerva Mobile Home Park—here is where you get your serene haven, where you connect, and thrive.
Contact Us
